  Fixed speex problem. Bug 97316.
  Cleanup ebuild.

  06 Oct 2005; MATSUU Takuto <matsuu@gentoo.org> vorbis-tools-1.0-r2.ebuild,
  vorbis-tools-1.0.1.ebuild, vorbis-tools-1.0.1-r1.ebuild,
